### Test Cursor Pagination - List Users API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Lấy trang đầu tiên (20 users đầu tiên)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Trang tiếp theo (dùng afterCursor từ response trên)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?limit=20&afterCursor=CURSOR_FROM_PREVIOUS_RESPONSE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Trang trước (dùng beforeCursor)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?limit=20&beforeCursor=CURSOR_FROM_RESPONSE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Search users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?search=john&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Filter by role
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?roleId=2&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Filter by company
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?companyId=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Filter active users only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?isActive=true&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Order ASC
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?order=ASC&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Combined filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?search=admin&roleId=2&isActive=true&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Large page (max 100)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Small page
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

